Additionally, you can enable <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://01.org/blogs/2014/running-average-power-limit-%E2%80%93-rapl">Running Average Power Limit ã RAPL</a> technology. Both <a href="/wiki/PowerTOP" title="PowerTOP">PowerTOP</a> and <a href="/index.php?title=Turbostat&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Turbostat (page does not exist)">turbostat</a> utilities are aware of RAPL. For RAPL enablement use:
